Reviews.original: The artwork features a moderate variety of line textures. The lines used to outline the figures and objects are generally consistent and clear, but there is a lack of intricate detail and variation in the line work. The background and the fish show some attempt at texture, but overall, the execution could benefit from more diversity in line styles to enhance the visual interest and depth of the piece.
